4Geeks Academy offers a course in Applied Artificial Intelligence that is designed for professionals looking to integrate AI into their work. The course covers various topics such as generative AI, context, prompts, and models. It is a 6-week program that includes 2 live online classes per week. The class size is limited to 12 people and there are no prerequisites or previous experience required. Upon completion, participants will receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. For more information, visit their website at [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop